# Windsurf Rules Bridge

Use [AGENT.md](AGENT.md) as the canonical policy for this repository.

## Required Defaults

1. Preserve DDD and Hexagonal boundaries.
2. Keep controllers thin and use-case driven.
3. Use ACL gateways for cross-context operations.
4. Follow the standard workflow: Intake -> Plan -> Execute -> Verify -> Handoff.
5. Apply relevant skills from `.agents/skills/*/SKILL.md`.
6. Prioritize `.agents/skills/module-conventions-generator/SKILL.md` for generation/scaffolding.
